metadata.name: The Longbow Allegiance #1
metadata.description: The Longbow Allegiance is a collection of 1337 elite assassins who have attained legendary status, in their own fields of expertise. These highly skilled archers have been hand-picked from the most exceptional warriors around the world, brought together under a singular banner to achieve a common goal: the pursuit of justice and the creation of lasting change. With a reputation for operating in the shadows, these masters of stealth join together to deliver swift and precise justice in all forms. This NFT collection displays a collective of exceptional art and representation of the power within the allegiance.
